Summary: Very fast moving, translucent, rectangular object flying northeast to southwest with no sound production. No lights apparent.
divs: Sighting Details1. Eating dinner outside with family. 2. Father in law facing north. 3. Space shuttle in low orbit 4. Rectangular, transluscent, dull faced Moved extremely fast northeast to southwest while creating NO noise. Traveled on a straight path until out of view. Entire sighting took less than 40 seconds. 5. We were all baffled at what it could possibly be. Weve never seen anything move move that fast while creating not one sound. 6. Lost sight when object went out of view over trees in neighbors yard.
